會議英語




會議英語
|會議英語|演說用語1|演說用語2|會議用語1|會議用語2|
 


宣佈會議開始
Let's call the meeting to order.

揭示討論要點
Allow me to set out the main issues for you.

請(張先生)來發言
To discuss this matter, I'd like to call on Mr. Chang.

請(林先生)接著發言
Mr. Lin, I'd like you to take the floor.

表示同意或贊成
I agree with you.

表示不同意或不贊成
I'm sorry, but I don't agree with you.

表達支持看法
I'd like to support Mr. Chang's remarks

表達反對看法
I strongly oppose that plan.

詢問別人意見
Would anyone like to give their ideas on this?

 表達自己的見解
 The way I see it is that, first of all, …；second …

 請求詳細說明
 I wonder if you could clarify this point.

 宣佈會議結束
 The meeting is now closed.

 
